	<description>Crubik 2D is nice puzzle. You should play it on 2D surface. Just try new experience ;-)</description>
	<author href="http://webmotoric.com" email="oleksiy.nesterov+mobileapp@gmail.com">Oleksiy Nesterov, Webmotoric</author>

